---

## Usage Guidelines

While this project is released under the MIT License, users are encouraged to:

1. **Acknowledge the work:** Provide attribution when using or adapting this code
2. **Cite the research:** Reference the original PARC research paper that inspired the methodology
3. **Educational use:** This project was developed for educational purposes; validate and adapt for production use
4. **Synthetic data notice:** Be aware that all data used is synthetic (Synthea-generated) and may not reflect real-world fraud patterns
5. **Responsible AI:** Ensure any fraud detection system built from this work includes human oversight and fairness audits

